data.description: This charming home is situated in a great neighborhood near parks, shopping, & restaurants! The main level features beautiful hardwood flooring, 2 bedrooms, 2 living room spaces or a formal dining, wood beams, a gas FP, & stainless steel appliances. The upper level has a 3rd bedroom or additional living space. Lower level could be your 4th bedroom or a great family room space w/ a gas FP. Also includes a newer roof,  a big double garage, & a wonderful fenced-in backyard w/ a deck. Put your finishing touches on this cozy home. No outlet street & easy access to Hwy 694 & University Ave.
